WEBVTT

00:00:35.966 --> 00:00:38.633
=Angels and Guards=

00:00:38.633 --> 00:00:41.233
=Episode 27=

00:00:41.433 --> 00:00:43.366
Ming laws are made by imperial power.

00:00:43.400 --> 00:00:46.100
And you are trying to investigate
the very people who make them.

00:00:46.600 --> 00:00:47.933
Then, before imperial power,

00:00:47.933 --> 00:00:49.266
does justice mean nothing?

00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:54.700
Do you know what this is called?

00:00:55.666 --> 00:00:57.033
Defying your superiors.

00:00:57.733 --> 00:00:58.433
That is treasonous.

00:00:59.400 --> 00:01:01.433
Zhang Weimin, you are afraid.

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:05.766
How dare you!

00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:13.966
Guards!

00:01:14.366 --> 00:01:15.200
Guards!

00:01:16.533 --> 00:01:16.900
Guards!

00:01:18.600 --> 00:01:19.100
My lord.

00:01:20.100 --> 00:01:20.666
How dare you, Shen Bingfan!

00:01:20.933 --> 00:01:21.966
Did you just defy the Commander?

00:01:22.166 --> 00:01:22.733
Do you know your crime?

00:01:24.366 --> 00:01:25.400
I'm only trying to solve the case.

00:01:25.566 --> 00:01:26.266
What crime have I committed?

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:27.733
But you,

00:01:28.366 --> 00:01:30.233
all you do is protect yourselves
and shrink back.

00:01:30.600 --> 00:01:31.533
So let me ask you.

00:01:31.766 --> 00:01:32.600
In your eyes,

00:01:33.333 --> 00:01:34.666
which matters more, law and justice,

00:01:35.233 --> 00:01:36.400
or your rank, pay, and future?

00:01:36.733 --> 00:01:37.633
Hear that? Hear that?

00:01:38.033 --> 00:01:39.100
Unbelievable.

00:01:39.233 --> 00:01:41.933
Her tongue is getting sharper
by the day.

00:01:42.266 --> 00:01:42.866
What do you know?

00:01:43.433 --> 00:01:45.200
You think blind recklessness
can solve a case?

00:01:46.166 --> 00:01:47.366
You have no sense of the bigger picture.

00:01:48.933 --> 00:01:50.333
Fine, Mr. Lu.

00:01:50.900 --> 00:01:51.733
Then let me ask you.

00:01:52.266 --> 00:01:55.166
Was it your so-called bigger picture

00:01:55.600 --> 00:01:56.933
that framed my father, Shen Lian?

00:01:59.033 --> 00:01:59.700
What did you say?

00:02:00.566 --> 00:02:01.966
How dare you bring up
what happened back then?

00:02:02.533 --> 00:02:03.400
Since I have,

00:02:04.166 --> 00:02:05.500
I will pursue it to the end.

00:02:06.733 --> 00:02:08.500
I ask you, two lords,
to tell me the truth.

00:02:11.533 --> 00:02:12.366
You really want to know?

00:02:12.566 --> 00:02:13.133
Guokai.

00:02:16.733 --> 00:02:17.166
My lord.

00:02:18.333 --> 00:02:19.333
Since Miss Shen has asked,

00:02:20.100 --> 00:02:22.433
and this matter has weighed on me
for many years,

00:02:23.033 --> 00:02:23.700
today,

00:02:24.100 --> 00:02:25.633
I might as well tell her the truth.

00:02:29.433 --> 00:02:30.166
Seven years ago,

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:32.033
Prince Luo's rebellion was crushed.

00:02:32.900 --> 00:02:34.966
Many people at court were implicated.

00:02:35.866 --> 00:02:37.200
(Shen and I received
a secret imperial order)

00:02:37.700 --> 00:02:38.533
(to protect a witness,)

00:02:38.733 --> 00:02:40.566
(Xu Wenchang, steward of Prince Luo's
manor, on his way to the capital.)

00:02:41.366 --> 00:02:43.233
(He was to identify Prince Luo's
accomplices in the capital.)

00:02:43.933 --> 00:02:46.833
(Qianhu Shen Lian escorted Xu Wenchang
and his wife)

00:02:47.400 --> 00:02:49.300
(through the wilderness.)

00:02:50.666 --> 00:02:51.333
But it was you

00:02:51.500 --> 00:02:53.333
and Wang Yan, who were supposed
to receive my father but betrayed him,

00:02:54.100 --> 00:02:56.000
and that is why he and the witness
were killed by Leng Xin.

00:02:56.333 --> 00:02:58.066
I didn't! I swear I didn't!

00:02:58.766 --> 00:02:59.966
I was determined to receive him.

00:03:00.833 --> 00:03:01.233
But

00:03:02.000 --> 00:03:03.166
the map I had was fake.

00:03:03.866 --> 00:03:04.400
What?

00:03:23.033 --> 00:03:23.766
(Weird.)

00:03:32.333 --> 00:03:33.033
What does that mean?

00:03:33.500 --> 00:03:34.000
Back then,

00:03:34.366 --> 00:03:34.766
I,

00:03:35.033 --> 00:03:35.400
your father,

00:03:35.733 --> 00:03:36.233
and Wang Yan

00:03:36.533 --> 00:03:37.700
each had

00:03:37.833 --> 00:03:38.333
a different route map.

00:03:39.066 --> 00:03:39.900
How could that be?

00:03:40.600 --> 00:03:42.100
When I reached
the correct rendezvous point,

00:03:42.533 --> 00:03:43.466
I found your father,

00:03:43.766 --> 00:03:44.833
Xu Wenchang, and his wife

00:03:45.733 --> 00:03:46.400
all dead.

00:03:47.933 --> 00:03:49.200
Who gave you that map?

00:03:49.266 --> 00:03:50.200
I did.

00:03:51.533 --> 00:03:51.966
You?

00:03:52.200 --> 00:03:52.733
Yes.

00:03:53.766 --> 00:03:54.533
I personally

00:03:55.533 --> 00:03:58.300
handed the route maps to your father.

00:03:59.200 --> 00:04:02.066
The Jinyiwei value thorough planning
above all.

00:04:02.400 --> 00:04:03.133
So

00:04:03.600 --> 00:04:05.600
I gave your father

00:04:05.933 --> 00:04:07.100
three routes to the capital

00:04:07.533 --> 00:04:09.566
and asked him to choose

00:04:09.733 --> 00:04:11.600
the safest

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:13.533
and most secret one.

00:04:13.933 --> 00:04:14.700
Then that means

00:04:15.900 --> 00:04:16.666
this route

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:19.000
was chosen by my father himself.

00:04:19.166 --> 00:04:19.600
Yes.

00:04:20.433 --> 00:04:22.800
Your father was the Commander
of this operation.

00:04:23.433 --> 00:04:24.833
Guokai and Wang Yan

00:04:25.233 --> 00:04:27.066
had to follow his orders.

00:04:27.566 --> 00:04:28.933
The route

00:04:29.333 --> 00:04:31.533
and rendezvous point

00:04:31.933 --> 00:04:33.033
were chosen by your father himself.

00:04:35.266 --> 00:04:37.100
Then who gave you the false route map?

00:04:39.366 --> 00:04:40.133
Your father did.

00:04:52.033 --> 00:04:53.700
My father would never take the wrong map

00:04:54.066 --> 00:04:55.766
and put himself and the witness
in danger.

00:04:56.066 --> 00:04:56.966
Someone must have switched it.

00:04:57.166 --> 00:04:58.100
Even if someone did,

00:04:58.366 --> 00:04:59.600
the mistake happened
on your father's side.

00:05:05.400 --> 00:05:06.166
There is one more thing

00:05:07.100 --> 00:05:08.100
I need to make clear to you.

00:05:08.566 --> 00:05:10.966
The Commander of the Northern Bureau
back then

00:05:11.266 --> 00:05:13.200
was Chang Beiming's elder brother,

00:05:13.233 --> 00:05:13.900
Chang Beixiao.

00:05:16.233 --> 00:05:17.333
His Majesty ordered him

00:05:17.566 --> 00:05:18.400
to train at the Northern Bureau.

00:05:19.566 --> 00:05:20.233
What?

00:05:20.400 --> 00:05:21.000
Guokai.

00:05:22.533 --> 00:05:23.266
Enough.

00:05:25.933 --> 00:05:26.333
My lord.

00:05:27.866 --> 00:05:28.900
Since I have started,

00:05:29.400 --> 00:05:31.500
please let me say it all.

00:05:35.100 --> 00:05:37.500
This mission was assigned
by Chang Beixiao himself.

00:05:37.933 --> 00:05:39.866
Qianhu Shen was personally appointed
by Chang Beixiao, too.

00:05:40.366 --> 00:05:41.433
After Qianhu Shen's death,

00:05:41.833 --> 00:05:44.266
Chang Beixiao was ambushed
inside the Northern Bureau.

00:05:44.266 --> 00:05:45.533
He was struck from behind
and gravely wounded,

00:05:45.866 --> 00:05:47.066
leaving him crippled for life.

00:05:47.566 --> 00:05:48.300
Otherwise,

00:05:48.666 --> 00:05:50.666
how could Chang Beiming,
the capital's greatest playboy,

00:05:51.033 --> 00:05:52.966
have become heir to Duke Zheng?

00:05:54.333 --> 00:05:55.333
They even dared

00:05:55.333 --> 00:05:57.866
to attack the Commander
of the Northern Bureau!

00:06:00.033 --> 00:06:01.400
This matter

00:06:02.000 --> 00:06:03.166
is quite complicated.

00:06:04.200 --> 00:06:07.100
It involves many factions,
both at court and beyond.

00:06:07.833 --> 00:06:10.233
At the time, the Crown Prince
had only just been confirmed.

00:06:10.733 --> 00:06:11.333
Prince Fu

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:13.433
was watching hungrily from the side.

00:06:14.033 --> 00:06:16.966
The court officials didn't want
to stir up more trouble.

00:06:17.900 --> 00:06:20.300
The Cabinet only wanted stability.

00:06:20.833 --> 00:06:22.700
So they kept this case

00:06:23.500 --> 00:06:24.700
sealed for years

00:06:25.933 --> 00:06:26.666
and made your father

00:06:27.900 --> 00:06:29.000
take the blame.

00:06:36.866 --> 00:06:37.933
Understood?

00:06:38.400 --> 00:06:39.233
Many things

00:06:39.433 --> 00:06:41.300
can't be touched without shaking
the whole court,

00:06:41.866 --> 00:06:42.600
So,

00:06:43.100 --> 00:06:45.133
we can't risk everything

00:06:45.500 --> 00:06:46.733
just to catch Leng Xin.

00:06:47.766 --> 00:06:48.633
Prince Luo's rebellion

00:06:49.200 --> 00:06:50.233
shook the entire court.

00:06:50.666 --> 00:06:51.400
It nearly became

00:06:51.533 --> 00:06:53.733
a weapon for men with hidden agendas,

00:06:54.266 --> 00:06:56.100
a pretext for a bloody purge.

00:06:56.866 --> 00:06:59.100
The court has only just settled down.

00:06:59.566 --> 00:07:01.766
If we reopen Leng Xin's case now,

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:05.100
we will be stepping straight
into the mire of Meizhen House.

00:07:06.366 --> 00:07:08.700
And if Prince Fu is pulled into it,

00:07:09.366 --> 00:07:10.700
there will be

00:07:12.233 --> 00:07:13.600
bloodshed all over again.

00:07:14.933 --> 00:07:16.433
But the truth is inside Meizhen House.

00:07:16.900 --> 00:07:18.233
Leng Xin is inside Meizhen House.

00:07:19.766 --> 00:07:20.800
If we don't catch him,

00:07:21.766 --> 00:07:22.433
the truth

00:07:22.933 --> 00:07:24.800
will stay buried forever.

00:07:27.166 --> 00:07:27.866
Bingfan.

00:07:28.666 --> 00:07:30.766
Why must you be so stubborn?

00:07:31.066 --> 00:07:32.900
Must you go after Meizhen House?

00:07:33.333 --> 00:07:34.233
Commander,

00:07:35.000 --> 00:07:37.033
don't you want to know
who betrayed the Jinyiwei?

00:07:37.166 --> 00:07:38.433
Don't make accusations without proof.

00:07:38.833 --> 00:07:40.000
The proof is in Meizhen House.

00:07:40.333 --> 00:07:41.366
And Leng Xin is the witness.

00:07:41.833 --> 00:07:43.666
Back then, even you could not
produce the true route map.

00:07:43.933 --> 00:07:45.000
How did Leng Xin know the route?

00:07:45.566 --> 00:07:46.566
Catch him,

00:07:47.200 --> 00:07:47.900
find out why,

00:07:48.533 --> 00:07:50.133
and the truth comes out.

00:07:52.033 --> 00:07:53.100
Have you thought about what comes after?

00:07:55.600 --> 00:07:56.333
You are saying that

00:07:57.266 --> 00:07:59.166
because you fear it will lead
to Prince Fu

00:07:59.366 --> 00:08:00.300
and become impossible to contain.

00:08:00.366 --> 00:08:01.366
Since you know that,

00:08:01.566 --> 00:08:02.900
why are you still rushing in?

00:08:03.166 --> 00:08:04.733
What if Prince Fu really is behind it?

00:08:05.766 --> 00:08:08.333
Will you two let the case
stay buried forever?

00:08:08.666 --> 00:08:09.333
How dare you!

00:08:09.866 --> 00:08:11.266
This is outrageous.

00:08:11.833 --> 00:08:13.200
I have explained all this to you,

00:08:13.366 --> 00:08:14.400
and not only do you refuse
to understand,

00:08:14.600 --> 00:08:15.800
but you also keep pushing harder.

00:08:16.433 --> 00:08:18.266
You are merely

00:08:18.500 --> 00:08:20.500
a Baihu under my Northern Bureau.

00:08:20.833 --> 00:08:22.666
This is insubordination!

00:08:25.833 --> 00:08:26.566
You are driving me mad!

00:08:27.933 --> 00:08:30.133
I hereby order that from today on,

00:08:30.566 --> 00:08:33.566
all three female Jinyiwei
are suspended for reflection,

00:08:33.900 --> 00:08:34.933
pending further conduct!

00:08:35.400 --> 00:08:36.666
Pending further conduct!

00:08:38.066 --> 00:08:40.566
I caused the trouble.
Why suspend all three of us?

00:08:42.766 --> 00:08:43.633
Because I want to!

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:45.200
I'm the Commander.

00:08:45.433 --> 00:08:46.700
Are you the Commander?

00:08:47.033 --> 00:08:47.633
I want to!

00:08:47.900 --> 00:08:48.800
I want to!

00:08:55.166 --> 00:08:55.533
You...

00:08:57.100 --> 00:08:57.533
How dare you!

00:08:58.266 --> 00:08:59.333
Who are you throwing that at?

00:09:00.833 --> 00:09:01.600
At me, my lord.

00:09:01.866 --> 00:09:03.433
Who are you taking it out on?

00:09:03.600 --> 00:09:04.466
Me, my lord. Please calm down.

00:09:05.400 --> 00:09:06.166
My lord.

00:09:06.733 --> 00:09:07.433
Is it damaged?

00:09:08.566 --> 00:09:09.733
And you.

00:09:10.433 --> 00:09:11.333
Why provoke her?

00:09:11.733 --> 00:09:12.933
Why dig up the past?

00:09:13.100 --> 00:09:15.533
What good did that do?

00:09:18.100 --> 00:09:18.500
My lord.

00:09:19.333 --> 00:09:21.100
This has weighed on me for years.

00:09:21.900 --> 00:09:23.500
Today, in front of my old friend's
daughter,

00:09:24.600 --> 00:09:25.966
I only wanted to get it off my chest.

00:09:26.033 --> 00:09:28.200
Get it off your chest,
get it off your chest...

00:09:28.533 --> 00:09:29.200
I'm telling you,

00:09:29.333 --> 00:09:30.333
one day,

00:09:30.500 --> 00:09:32.766
you people will tear a hole in the sky.

00:09:34.900 --> 00:09:35.800
Officials shielding officials.

00:09:36.033 --> 00:09:36.866
Twisting the law for their own gain.

00:09:37.600 --> 00:09:38.300
Ridiculous.

00:09:38.833 --> 00:09:41.166
Something feels wrong

00:09:41.166 --> 00:09:42.500
about suspending all three of us
over Meizhen House.

00:09:43.666 --> 00:09:44.733
It is suspicious.

00:09:45.400 --> 00:09:46.100
Hua.

00:09:46.500 --> 00:09:47.866
What exactly is suspicious?

00:09:48.266 --> 00:09:50.300
If I knew exactly what was wrong,

00:09:50.533 --> 00:09:51.566
it would not be suspicious.

00:09:54.833 --> 00:09:55.266
Bingfan.

00:09:56.833 --> 00:09:57.666
Come outside with me.

00:10:03.566 --> 00:10:05.300
Bingfan, listen to me.

00:10:05.766 --> 00:10:06.800
Don't investigate Meizhen House.

00:10:07.533 --> 00:10:08.900
But Leng Xin is hiding there.

00:10:09.400 --> 00:10:10.133
Just

00:10:10.666 --> 00:10:12.166
stay away from that place.

00:10:14.200 --> 00:10:14.766
So in the end,

00:10:15.700 --> 00:10:17.033
you are all still afraid of Prince Fu.

00:10:19.433 --> 00:10:20.766
Think whatever you want.

00:10:21.933 --> 00:10:23.000
Just don't do anything rash.

00:10:24.933 --> 00:10:26.500
Don't you want to know

00:10:26.766 --> 00:10:27.800
who harmed your brother?

00:10:30.500 --> 00:10:31.400
Who told you that?

00:10:36.400 --> 00:10:37.400
You disappoint me.

00:11:04.366 --> 00:11:04.800
It's you.

00:11:05.533 --> 00:11:05.866
Yes.

00:11:08.033 --> 00:11:09.133
You are not here

00:11:09.166 --> 00:11:10.066
to talk me out of Meizhen House, too,
are you?

00:11:10.733 --> 00:11:11.566
I don't know what to say.

00:11:13.333 --> 00:11:14.200
I just wanted to stay with you.

00:11:15.666 --> 00:11:17.500
A place even the Jinyiwei
dare not touch.

00:11:18.866 --> 00:11:19.900
A place above the law.

00:11:20.766 --> 00:11:22.200
A shelter for every crime.

00:11:23.833 --> 00:11:25.533
How are ordinary people
supposed to live?

00:11:26.533 --> 00:11:27.766
Where is justice in any of this?

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:32.866
Before I joined the Ministry of Justice,

00:11:34.833 --> 00:11:36.066
I believed I could catch criminals,

00:11:36.666 --> 00:11:38.100
solve cases, and win justice
for the people.

00:11:40.033 --> 00:11:40.966
But later I learned

00:11:42.033 --> 00:11:43.066
that the people I arrested

00:11:43.766 --> 00:11:45.300
only needed a bit of powerful backing,

00:11:46.500 --> 00:11:48.233
and they would walk free.

00:11:52.333 --> 00:11:53.933
But I never thought of giving up.

00:11:55.500 --> 00:11:56.666
I will catch them.

00:11:58.333 --> 00:11:59.100
I will find enough evidence

00:11:59.766 --> 00:12:00.800
that they can't argue,

00:12:01.333 --> 00:12:02.100
and they can't run.

00:12:04.666 --> 00:12:06.233
That is the only thing I can do.

00:12:11.666 --> 00:12:13.033
I have to investigate Meizhen House.

00:12:14.200 --> 00:12:15.400
Even if I do it alone,

00:12:16.500 --> 00:12:17.333
I will do it.

00:12:19.266 --> 00:12:20.133
I'm investigating Meizhen House.

00:12:20.366 --> 00:12:21.533
Who is with me? Who is against me?

00:12:21.933 --> 00:12:22.333
I'm with you.

00:12:22.666 --> 00:12:23.266
So am I.

00:12:23.666 --> 00:12:24.366
Are you sure?

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:26.833
Even if it is a wolf's den,

00:12:27.833 --> 00:12:28.833
I want to see it for myself.

00:12:29.166 --> 00:12:30.400
But we have all

00:12:31.000 --> 00:12:32.333
been suspended.

00:12:32.700 --> 00:12:34.600
What authority do we have
to investigate them?

00:12:34.866 --> 00:12:36.133
We are only suspended,

00:12:36.533 --> 00:12:37.366
not dismissed.

00:12:37.900 --> 00:12:40.733
Am I not still a Jinyiwei Baihu?

00:12:41.700 --> 00:12:42.600
I have always felt

00:12:42.933 --> 00:12:44.533
there is more to the Commander's move.

00:12:44.900 --> 00:12:46.266
His words were harsh,

00:12:46.533 --> 00:12:48.266
but he left us a way forward.

00:12:48.700 --> 00:12:49.800
You have been suspended,

00:12:50.333 --> 00:12:51.266
but as Bingfan said,

00:12:51.700 --> 00:12:53.033
you were not dismissed,

00:12:53.533 --> 00:12:54.766
and your movements were not restricted.

00:12:55.900 --> 00:12:57.433
You mean

00:12:57.933 --> 00:13:01.133
that old man wants us
to test Meizhen House

00:13:01.333 --> 00:13:03.333
in our own names?

00:13:03.333 --> 00:13:04.366
It is possible.

00:13:05.166 --> 00:13:07.266
If we go under the Northern Bureau's
name,

00:13:08.033 --> 00:13:09.633
and trouble breaks out later,

00:13:10.366 --> 00:13:11.800
there will be no room to step back.

00:13:13.033 --> 00:13:14.433
But to investigate Meizhen House,

00:13:14.833 --> 00:13:17.333
we need a flawless plan.

00:13:18.900 --> 00:13:19.433
Duoyu.

00:13:20.033 --> 00:13:20.566
I'll leave this job to you.

00:13:21.400 --> 00:13:23.600
I will disguise myself
and scout the way first.

00:13:27.566 --> 00:13:29.133
The doors are shut
even in broad daylight.

00:13:29.566 --> 00:13:31.300
We can't get in by ordinary means.

00:13:31.600 --> 00:13:32.433
In my experience,

00:13:33.266 --> 00:13:34.133
there is only one way.

00:13:35.400 --> 00:13:35.833
Act arrogant.

00:13:36.566 --> 00:13:37.266
What does that mean?

00:13:38.233 --> 00:13:39.900
High officials, nobles,
imperial relatives...

00:13:40.433 --> 00:13:42.666
They all swagger around
like they own the world.

00:13:44.100 --> 00:13:44.800
When you go in,

00:13:45.566 --> 00:13:47.466
curse whoever stops you
and hit whoever gets in your way.

00:13:47.833 --> 00:13:49.433
They will think you are too powerful
to offend,

00:13:49.833 --> 00:13:50.766
with a terrifying background.

00:13:51.233 --> 00:13:52.166
Then they may let you in.

00:13:52.833 --> 00:13:54.533
That could actually work.

00:13:56.233 --> 00:13:57.100
I will wait here.

00:13:58.033 --> 00:13:59.100
You have half an hour.

00:13:59.766 --> 00:14:00.166
That's enough.

00:14:01.266 --> 00:14:01.633
Who is it?

00:14:06.266 --> 00:14:07.000
Who are you looking for?

00:14:10.100 --> 00:14:10.666
You...

00:14:12.233 --> 00:14:13.733
Forgive us. Sir, who are you?

00:14:14.600 --> 00:14:15.600
Who are you?

00:14:15.866 --> 00:14:16.700
You are not worthy to speak to me.

00:14:17.066 --> 00:14:18.000
Get your manager out.

00:14:21.766 --> 00:14:22.600
Sir.

00:14:22.833 --> 00:14:23.900
Such a temper.

00:14:24.433 --> 00:14:26.300
I'm Zheng Lun, front hall steward
of Meizhen House.

00:14:26.433 --> 00:14:27.466
(Zheng Lun, steward of Meizhen House)
Greetings.

00:14:27.467 --> 00:14:29.866
(Zheng Lun, steward of Meizhen House)

00:14:31.833 --> 00:14:33.566
I don't think I have seen you before.

00:14:34.233 --> 00:14:35.833
You are not a regular guest, are you?

00:14:37.266 --> 00:14:37.833
Why?

00:14:38.266 --> 00:14:39.866
Does Meizhen House only admit regulars?

00:14:40.366 --> 00:14:43.733
Correct. Meizhen House is not open
to the public.

00:14:44.033 --> 00:14:45.366
It is a private gathering place.

00:14:45.766 --> 00:14:48.433
All honored guests must present
a jade token.

00:14:49.900 --> 00:14:50.600
What jade token?

00:14:53.600 --> 00:14:54.700
This.

00:14:56.733 --> 00:14:58.233
I'm new. I don't have one.

00:14:59.200 --> 00:14:59.700
New?

00:15:00.900 --> 00:15:02.733
Then you must have a letter
of introduction.

00:15:04.900 --> 00:15:05.433
What letter?

00:15:05.566 --> 00:15:06.733
Proof of which honored guest

00:15:06.733 --> 00:15:08.966
recommended you to Meizhen House.

00:15:09.400 --> 00:15:11.300
Do you know Feng Zhihe?

00:15:12.333 --> 00:15:13.366
Eunuch Feng's nephew.

00:15:14.000 --> 00:15:15.166
And Shizhen and Ye Ping?

00:15:17.333 --> 00:15:18.166
The sons of the Grand Secretary

00:15:18.600 --> 00:15:20.333
and the Minister of War?

00:15:20.666 --> 00:15:21.400
Do you still need to ask?

00:15:23.700 --> 00:15:24.800
Forgive me for failing to recognize you.

00:15:25.200 --> 00:15:26.066
Take this gentleman to...

00:15:26.566 --> 00:15:28.300
I will personally escort you
to the back.

00:15:28.866 --> 00:15:29.700
This way, sir.

00:15:34.100 --> 00:15:34.966
Please.

00:15:48.666 --> 00:15:50.000
This way, sir.

00:15:59.900 --> 00:16:01.933
Watch your step.

00:16:02.866 --> 00:16:03.300
Please.

00:16:04.666 --> 00:16:05.333
It is inside.

00:16:09.100 --> 00:16:09.666
Sir.

00:16:10.033 --> 00:16:10.866
Please follow me.

00:16:13.866 --> 00:16:14.400
Sir.

00:16:14.900 --> 00:16:15.400
This way.

00:16:31.500 --> 00:16:32.400
I missed you so much.

00:16:34.000 --> 00:16:34.600
My lord.

00:16:34.833 --> 00:16:35.366
Cheers.

00:16:42.000 --> 00:16:42.500
Open the door.

00:17:17.200 --> 00:17:17.933
Open your mouth.

00:17:17.933 --> 00:17:18.500
Sure.

00:17:28.600 --> 00:17:32.166
What is a female Jinyiwei
from the Northern Bureau doing here?

00:17:34.000 --> 00:17:36.033
My lord, does that feel good?

00:17:36.166 --> 00:17:37.266
Very good.

00:17:41.100 --> 00:17:41.600
Sir.

00:17:41.866 --> 00:17:42.233
Please.

00:17:43.733 --> 00:17:44.300
This way.

00:17:44.400 --> 00:17:45.833
Come on. Let's drink.

00:17:48.900 --> 00:17:49.900
Is it sweet?

00:17:50.700 --> 00:17:51.566
Have another.

00:17:54.866 --> 00:17:55.300
Duan.

00:17:55.700 --> 00:17:56.700
You have only had a few cups,

00:17:56.700 --> 00:17:57.533
and you have already gone

00:17:57.733 --> 00:17:58.300
to the privy three times.

00:17:58.766 --> 00:17:59.700
Careful,

00:18:00.033 --> 00:18:01.200
or the beauties will think
you can't keep up.

00:18:02.166 --> 00:18:02.700
My lord.

00:18:03.833 --> 00:18:04.666
Please step aside.

00:18:05.866 --> 00:18:06.400
Step aside?

00:18:06.400 --> 00:18:07.333
Why so mysterious?

00:18:10.100 --> 00:18:11.166
Ladies, wait for me.

00:18:15.900 --> 00:18:16.400
My lord.

00:18:17.233 --> 00:18:18.600
Come see what is happening outside.

00:18:22.400 --> 00:18:22.966
My lord.

00:18:23.766 --> 00:18:26.266
Would you like a change
of company tonight?

00:18:46.666 --> 00:18:49.833
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

00:18:50.200 --> 00:18:53.566
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

00:18:53.833 --> 00:18:56.833
♪My heart drifted lost♪

00:18:56.833 --> 00:19:00.233
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

00:19:01.333 --> 00:19:04.533
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

00:19:04.966 --> 00:19:08.300
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

00:19:08.866 --> 00:19:11.066
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

00:19:11.100 --> 00:19:15.133
♪I've softly let it go♪

00:19:15.133 --> 00:19:19.000
♪The vow you made was true♪

00:19:19.000 --> 00:19:22.733
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

00:19:23.033 --> 00:19:24.933
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

00:19:24.966 --> 00:19:29.500
♪And forget at world's end♪

00:19:29.800 --> 00:19:31.300
♪Embracing memory♪

00:19:31.300 --> 00:19:33.666
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

00:19:33.666 --> 00:19:37.533
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

00:19:37.533 --> 00:19:39.833
♪I wish to let it pass♪

00:19:39.866 --> 00:19:44.866
♪And run toward this vast life♪